txt.en: Shíktarb is at Shrak Mauruk.\n\nYou should listen to Shíktarb yell at you.
'Can you believe those Men put up rickety barricades to keep us out?! Foolish!\n\n'Go destroy them, they look stupid. They don't understand the power of the Morgul army! Show them what we are!'
Shíktarb commands you to destroy enemy barricades scattered around Western Osgiliath to dismantle the Gondorian defences.
'Destruction is what I like to hear! Keep at it you peon. There might be hope for you yet to rise through the ranks!'
Enemy barricades can be found on the Western side of Osgiliath.\n\nDestroy the enemy barricades.
